  m_text: 'Investigation of the once inhabited village allowed for the discovery
    of evidence that suggests what events may have occured.


    Sustained damage
    was apparent althroughout much greater than weather alone could cause, suggesting
    a raid that was performed.


    Alongside this, a piece of a cloth featuring
    a distinct symbol identical to that found painted on the dome after the event,
    confirming that this group were the perpetrators of this raid.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ab72a9c75c8230a4b9c3ea02b05222c8, type: 2}
